# ex:ts=8
# Ports collection makefile for:  bibcard
# Version required:     	  0.6.4
# Date created:			  Mon Feb 03, 1997
# Whom:				  David O'Brien (obrien@FreeBSD.org)
#
# $Id: Makefile,v 1.3 1997/04/15 04:58:06 obrien Exp $
